If you deploy multiple instance of the same application it doesn&#39;t help to distribute because message are publishing into one partition as you mentioned and only one instance will only be assigned to that partition other instances will just be idle.

2. You can use AdminClient Kafka API to check if any lagging on your consumer 

        Properties props = new Properties();
